@c ----------------------------------------------------------------------
@node xfree, memory
@subheading Syntax

@example
#include <stdlib.h>

void xfree(void *ptr);
@end example

@subheading Description

Frees memory allocated by @code{xmalloc} (@pxref{xmalloc}).  This
function guarantees that a NULL pointer is handled gracefully.

@subheading Example

@example
void *f = xmalloc(100);
xfree(f);
@end example

